<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>103</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>nǐ zǒu lái wǒ zǒu lái tā zǒu lái 迦南103</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ zǒu lái, wǒ zǒu lái, tā zǒu lái, bù shì ǒu rán hé qiǎo yù, shì shén de ān pái,
 lái zì sì miàn bā fāng, wǔ hú sì hǎi, wǒ men hǎo xiàng hěn shú xī, xiāng qīn xiāng ài
 duō jī dòng yòng yán yǔ wú fǎ biǎo bái, shén ràng wǒ men shēng zhǎng zài tóng yī gè shí dài,
 dēng shàng le zhēn lǐ de jiē tī rén shēng fàng guāng cǎi, jīn tiān de xiāng jù nán wàng huái nán wàng huái.</lyrics>
</song>